Package: COLDNet
Type: Package
Title: A generalized package for building interactive networks from dataframes using igraph, ggraph, visnetwork, and shiny.
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Kyle Gellatly
Maintainer: Kyle Gellatly <kyle.gellatly@umassmed.edu>
Description: From any input dataframe, this package can build interactive networks.
    The only requirement is that the associated data has 2 columns, one associated with edge colors, and the other the edge width.
License: TBD
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 2.10.0),
    igraph,
    visNetwork,
    ggplot2,
    ggraph,
    shiny,
    RColorBrewer
Imports:
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
